{"id": 2599, "genre": 1001, "title": "你最近遇到过哪些“虽然不算啥但总会让人掉血 1%”的日常小事？", "description": "来说说生活中那些引起“小确丧”的细枝末节。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Sky_melody）", "record_count": 5952, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181102020953ou4dLYFz2SsKBixf.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-11-08T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 309504, "content": "很长时间不带耳钉的耳洞堵住了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496866}, {"id": 310784, "content": "上完厕所，一按抽水马桶，水没下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1094978}, {"id": 309507, "content": "在医美充了几千块钱做了好几次了，但是今早突然发现没什么效果", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496874}, {"id": 310019, "content": "不会痛经被说成强壮：）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1498661}, {"id": 309508, "content": "想参与互动一下，才发现我一直是游客身份登录。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1344993}, {"id": 313093, "content": "同学把我不想透露的事情不小心说出去", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1511894}, {"id": 309510, "content": "选了个最短的队伍排队结账，结果还是比别的队伍慢…", "image": null, "praise_count": 251, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114444}, {"id": 309511, "content": "上班无聊，下班更无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 309512, "content": "刚买的皮鞋，地铁上被踩了一脚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148914}, {"id": 309768, "content": "一到图书馆发现忘带一本书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470961}, {"id": 309513, "content": "让座，别人没说谢谢", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496894}, {"id": 309515, "content": "💔选导师！！！各种bug＋意外", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1457639}, {"id": 309516, "content": "想睡睡不着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1489668}, {"id": 309517, "content": "梦到中了 500 万，醒了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 527389}, {"id": 309518, "content": "每天被别人硬接茬，啥样都接茬", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496909}, {"id": 311566, "content": "卡，各种卡不见\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1505891}, {"id": 309519, "content": "周末不想加班，成功了以后，在家感觉很无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481542}, {"id": 309775, "content": "在意的人取消了你的赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821351}, {"id": 309520, "content": "在听纯音乐的时候。总有人在旁边。而且说话声音很大", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1394116}, {"id": 309521, "content": "放假想上课，上课想放假", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496918}, {"id": 309522, "content": "被慢性咽炎折磨", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496704}, {"id": 309523, "content": "很开心穿了新鞋 每次都会下雨……", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1217088}, {"id": 309524, "content": "现在我在等火车 我头上正上方偏左貌似漏水（晴天）", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396508}, {"id": 310292, "content": "还花呗的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500531}, {"id": 309525, "content": "早上没早课，所以前一天晚上熬到凌晨两点多，结果第二天早上6点被噩梦吓醒，之后就再也睡不着了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1318135}, {"id": 314645, "content": "穿衣热，脱衣冷。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1434727}, {"id": 309527, "content": "傻呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494048}, {"id": 308248, "content": "下雨时走在路上，踩到一块松掉的地砖", "image": null, "praise_count": 852, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 309528, "content": "半夜总是被尿憋醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496946}, {"id": 308249, "content": "每天通勤时间长达四小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 126, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 309529, "content": "去洗手间大号起来的时候airpods裤子口袋里掉下来了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1480537}, {"id": 308250, "content": "加班回到家，泡杯面的时候汤溅到衣服上", "image": null, "praise_count": 180, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 309530, "content": "上课睡着了，睁开眼之后什么都听不懂了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496958}, {"id": 308251, "content": "周日晚上失眠，然而明早要开会", "image": null, "praise_count": 250, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 309531, "content": "起床(睡上铺)之后，发现眼镜落在床上了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1488079}, {"id": 309533, "content": "星期天要补课！！！还补一周课最多的那天…而那天异地恋的男友要来看我😭", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476136}, {"id": 311581, "content": "老板在群里面磕磕绊绊几十秒的语音", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1506045}, {"id": 312605, "content": "腰疼。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164682}, {"id": 309534, "content": "必须上台唱歌，本身歌唱不好很尴尬，手机还连不上话筒蓝牙，跟一个同学借，不给，但另一个同学上台唱歌时跟他借却给了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496972}, {"id": 310046, "content": "蓝牙耳机自动切了歌", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451316}, {"id": 309535, "content": "下雪天踩到一块被雪覆盖的光滑大理石路面", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852475}, {"id": 309536, "content": "末班公交做到了终点站", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323857}, {"id": 310048, "content": "刚给iphone换的电池，第二天电量40%自动关机，充电才能开机，店家让我再去换一次，然而来回又是半天时间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 530706}, {"id": 309537, "content": "和其他人的尴尬的对话", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1451953}, {"id": 309538, "content": "要考考试了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496987}, {"id": 310052, "content": "擦眼镜，多擦了一下，又脏了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391192}, {"id": 309541, "content": "帮大家买外卖，付钱的时候就没人搭理我", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312509}, {"id": 309542, "content": "科目二考了五次没过", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1496996}, {"id": 310054, "content": "出门后发现没带钥匙", "image": "img/option/option/20181110204802bv7KIteMf6zD9OXH", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1499007}, {"id": 315686, "content": "坐靠在转椅上，突然椅子向后仰\n安静的办公室突然想起刺耳的电话铃声，这样的感觉每一次的吓到心脏疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1527871}]}